<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Card Grid Layout</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:wght@400;500;700&family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-SnH5WK+bZxgPHs44uWIX+LLJAJ9/2PkPKZ5QiAj6Ta86w+fsb2TkcmfRyVX3pBnMFcV7oQPJkl9QevSCWr3W6A==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      color: #333;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .header {
      width: 100%;
      height: 12vh;
      background-color: #0f52ba;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
    }
    .container {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .card {
      background-color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
    .card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 200px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
    .card-content {
      padding: 1rem;
    }
    .card-title {
      font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #0f52ba;
    }
    .card-desc {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    Sectors & Industries
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='https://example.com'">
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Card Image">
      <div class="card-content">
        <h2 class="card-title">IT, ICT, Tech Industry, Software Development</h2>
        <p class="card-desc">The IT, ICT, and Tech industries encompass the development, management, and communication of technology and information, with software development focusing on creating applications and systems to enhance productivity and solve problems.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='https://example.com'">
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Card Image">
      <div class="card-content">
        <h2 class="card-title">Health Care, Medical Services</h2>
        <p class="card-desc">Healthcare, medical services, and medicine encompass prevention, diagnosis, and treatment of diseases, providing clinical care, diagnostics, and pharmaceutical solutions to enhance and maintain health and well-being.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='https://example.com'">
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Card Image">
      <div class="card-content">
        <h2 class="card-title">Finance, Banking, Investment, Accounting, Risk Management</h2>
        <p class="card-desc">Finance, banking, and accounting involve managing money, investments, risk management, and financial records to support financial growth, stability, and regulatory compliance for individuals and businesses.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='https://example.com'">
