      <div class="card-content">
        <h2 class="card-title">Engineering, Automotive, Infrastructure, Robotics, Construction</h2>
        <p class="card-desc">Engineering integrates scientific principles to design and innovate solutions across automotive, infrastructure, robotics, and construction sectors, shaping modern advancements and infrastructure critical for societal development and technological progress.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='https://example.com'">
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Card Image">
      <div class="card-content">
        <h2 class="card-title">Education, Research, Administration, Consulting</h2>
        <p class="card-desc">Education, research, administration, and consulting drive knowledge acquisition, innovation, and organizational efficiency. They foster learning, advance understanding through inquiry, manage operations, and provide expert guidance to enhance performance across diverse sectors.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='https://example.com'">
