      <div class="card-content">
        <h2 class="card-title">Technology, Consulting, Manufacturing, Healthcare</h2>
        <p class="card-desc">These industries encompass technology, manufacturing, finance, and healthcare, driving innovation, efficiency, financial stability, and healthcare delivery through roles in IT, operations, consulting, finance, and healthcare management.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='https://example.com'">
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Card Image">
      <div class="card-content">
