      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='https://example.com'">
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Card Image">
      <div class="card-content">
        <h2 class="card-title">Sustainability, Conservation, Geology & Hydrology, Infrastructure</h2>
        <p class="card-desc">Renewable energy and sustainability, environmental science and conservation, geology and hydrology, and green building and infrastructure focus on sustainable practices, environmental preservation, and resource management for a resilient future.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
